Imapcl - a simple CLI IMAP client for downloading email

Use example:

./imapcl imap.seznam.cz -a auth_file -o ./email_dir

where auth_file is a file containing user login information in this format:
'username
password'

CLI argument options:

-p Used port
-T use SSL/TLS encryption
-c certificate used for verification
-C directory where certificates are located
-n Only download new
-h only download headers
-a file with login information path
-b mailbox to download from
-o directory where emails are saved

Included files:
src/argparser.cpp
src/argparser.hpp
src/connection.cpp  
src/connection.hpp  
src/fileops.cpp  
